title: Christmas Short Works 2010
creator: Various
description: LibriVox 2010 Multilingual Christmas Short Works Collection. The collection contains public domain short stories, essays, poems and scripture passages recorded by a variety of LibriVox members in English, German and Portuguese. Details of the source text and readers may be found on the LibriVox catalogue page for this item. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org M4B format available
